    "Ahmad et al. [74] presented the study and parameters of the first-ever NER corpus for Shahmukhi script.",
    "To make up the latest produced corpus in which 16,300 identified entities and 318,275 tokens comprising 2,013 organizations, 3,140 places and 11,147 people.",
    "Additionally, the authors used five supervised learning approaches, including two cutting-edge deep learning techniques, to show that our corpus is usable.",
